::Shredder::

Shredder drags Quickstrike into the nearest room he sees, the door closing 
behind the two preds as he drags the fuzor in. Shredder tosses Quickstrike 
onto a bunch of crates, taking out his pistol and spinning it dangeroustly in 
his hand.

"I believe I owe you a good slagging," Shredder says, looking at Quickstrike 
to see how he'd react.
